<Body> 
	<Title>居民反映“天赐康缘”小区油烟噪音污染 环保执法人员现场查处6家饭店</Title>  
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014年04月21日 07:48:23</ReportTime>  
	<Content>
		<Paragraph> 
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent">接到
					<Participant sid="s1">群众</Participant>
					<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">反映</Denoter>
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e2">
					<Location lid="l2">“天赐康缘”小区</Location>
					<Object oid="o2">油烟噪音污染</Object>
					<Denoter did="d2" type="action">投诉</Denoter>
				</Event>后， 
				<Event eid="e3">
					<Time tid="t3" type="relTime">4月19日</Time>，
					<Participant sid="s3">市环保局小店分局</Participant>
					<Denoter did="d3" type="action">立即行动</Denoter>
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e4">对
					<Location lid="l4">该小区内</Location>的
					<Object oid="o4">6家饭店</Object>进行了
					<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">查处</Denoter>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>  
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e5">被投诉的
					<Object sid="s5">“天赐康缘”小区</Object>
					<Denoter did="d5" type="action">位于</Denoter>
					<Location lid="l5">小店区康宁街</Location>。
				</Event>
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent">
					<Participant sid="s6">执法人员</Participant>
					<Location lid="l6">现场</Location>
					<Denoter did="d6" type="statement">发现</Denoter>
				</Event>，“天赐康缘”1号楼一层就有6家饭店，分别为“琦傲”私家面馆、五寨面食馆、“天赐食府”、“一人一味”、“串串香”及 
				<Event eid="e7">一家
					<Denoter did="d7" type="operation">正在装修</Denoter>中的
					<Object oid="o7">饭店</Object>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e8">除
					<Participant sid="s8">“琦傲”私家面馆</Participant>
					<Denoter did="d8" type="action">已领取</Denoter>
					<Object oid="o8">餐饮服务许可证</Object>
				</Event>外，其余饭店均无任何合法证件。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e9">不过，
					<Participant sid="s9">该面馆</Participant>未
					<Denoter did="d9" type="action" polarity="negative">办理</Denoter>
					<Object oid="o9">环保相关手续</Object>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e10">而且，
					<Denoter did="d10" type="operation">正在运营</Denoter>的
					<Object oid="o10">5家饭店</Object>
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e11">
					<Object oid="o11,o12">油烟</Object>未经
					<Denoter did="d11" type="action" polarity="negative">处理</Denoter>
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e12">
					<Denoter did="d12" type="action">直接排放</Denoter>
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e13">
					<Object sid="s13">油烟污染</Object>
					<Denoter did="d13" type="emergency">影响</Denoter>到
					<Object oid="o13">小区居民的生活</Object>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e14">
					<Object sid="s14">饭店风机</Object>产生的
					<Denoter did="d14" type="emergency">噪音</Denoter>
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e15">也让一些
					<Participant sid="s15">居民</Participant>无法
					<Denoter did="d15" type="statement" polarity="negative">入眠</Denoter>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph> 
	</Content>  
